One of the most talked about Nigerian actresses at the moment, Regina Daniels, is set to host the Children’s Carnival in Delta. Regina Daniels, the current most-talked-about Nollywood actress on social media, is set to celeberate children on the occasion of this year’s Children Day, May 27, 2019. The event tagged, ‘Regina Daniels’ Children Day Carnival’ will hold at Government Field, Agbor, Delta State, The Nation reports. The actress whose age has been severally put at between 19 and 22 suddenly broke into the consciousness of Nigerians when she reportedly married 59 year old billionaire, Prince Ned Nwoko, had announced this on her Instagram account. “The Regina Daniels children’s day carnival is here again and it promises to be a fun filled event,” she wrote. Source